@startuml
title Viaverse Chat / Messaging — Class Model

class Conversation {
  id: ConversationId
  contextType: QUOTE | JOB | SUPPORT
  contextId: UUID
  status: ConversationStatus
  createdAt: Instant
  lastMessageAt: Instant?
}

class ConversationParticipant {
  conversationId: ConversationId
  accountId: AccountId
  role: REQUESTER | WORKER | BUSINESS | SUPPORT
  status: ParticipantStatus
  lastReadMessageId: MessageId?
}

class Message {
  id: MessageId
  conversationId: ConversationId
  senderAccountId: AccountId
  type: TEXT | MEDIA | SYSTEM
  body: String?
  status: MessageStatus
  createdAt: Instant
}

class MessageAttachment {
  messageId: MessageId
  mediaId: MediaId
  kind: IMAGE | VIDEO | FILE
  moderationStatus: MediaModerationStatus
}

class MessagingPolicy {
  canOpenConversation()
  canSendMessage()
  canAttachMedia()
  canShareContactInfo()
  canReport()
}

class SafetyDetection {
  id: UUID
  messageId: MessageId?
  detectionType: PHONE | EMAIL | ADDRESS | PAYMENT_BYPASS
  severity: Severity
  action: WARN | BLOCK | RISK_SIGNAL
}

class MessageReport {
  id: UUID
  messageId: MessageId
  reporterAccountId: AccountId
  reason: ReportReason
  status: ReportStatus
  createdAt: Instant
}

class MessagingEvents {
  ConversationCreated
  MessageSent
  MessageRead
  ContactSharingDetected
  MessageReported
  SupportEscalationRequested
}

Conversation "1" o-- "*" ConversationParticipant
Conversation "1" o-- "*" Message
Message "1" o-- "*" MessageAttachment
MessagingPolicy ..> Conversation : checks
MessagingPolicy ..> ConversationParticipant : checks
SafetyDetection ..> Message : scans
MessageReport ..> Message : reports
Message ..> MessagingEvents : emits
SafetyDetection ..> MessagingEvents : emits risk/safety
MessageReport ..> MessagingEvents : emits report

note bottom
Private chat content must not be used for ad targeting.
Admin/support access is scoped, reasoned and audited.
end note
@enduml
